reviewText:
Movie description: This out-of-print 1974 biker sleazefest is about:
A teacher and her four female students become stranded on the highway. Three bikers stop and offer assistance, but two of them turn out to be brutal killers. The bikers lead the girls to a deserted farm where they hold them hostage and teach them a lesson in terror. Do not let it go. Must see movie for action lovers.
